author: Lucy Craymer
title: Beef Prices Sizzle With U.S. Demand
text:
HONG KONG—Americans’ love of the humble hamburger and a good steak is keeping beef prices at records in Australia and New Zealand, even as China’s economic slowdown eats away at demand for other agricultural commodities.
